[[File:9envoys.jpg|thumb|250px|The green priest (far left).]]
The '''green priest''' was one of the [[High Elder]]s of the [[Order of the Sacred Circle]] on [[Monastery/Legends|Monastery]]. [[Gender/Legends|He]] accompanied the [[horned priest]] and [[Domina Tagge/Legends|Domina Tagge]] to [[Yavin 4/Legends|Yavin 4]] to bring [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] to Monastery.

The green priest was a [[Humanoid/Legends|humanoid]] with large [[Eye/Legends|eyes]], a head fin, and an overall somewhat [[Fish/Legends|fishlike]] face. He had smooth green skin and a flat [[Nose/Legends|nose]].

